### Get hardheads by userID
GET {{legacyHost}}/api/hardhead?userID=2630&code={{apiCode}}

### Get hardheads by dateFrom
GET {{legacyHost}}/api/hardhead?dateFrom=1.1.2020&code={{apiCode}}

### Get hardheads by nothing
GET {{legacyHost}}/api/hardhead?code={{apiCode}}

### Get hardhead actions
GET {{legacyHost}}/api/hardhead/5358/actions?code={{apiCode}}
